Titolo: BSS 01

Anno: 1980

Descrizione: The BSS 01 (short for Bildschirmspiel 01, meaning Screen Game 01 or Video Screen Game 01), also known as RFT TV-Spiel or simply TV-Spiel, is a dedicated first-generation home video game console that was released in 1980 or 1981 only in East Germany. It was manufactured between 1979 and 1980 by VEB Halbleiterwerk Frankfurt (Oder) and is credited the only video game console that was released in East Germany. Due to its high price, it rarely succeeded in private households and mostly delivered to youth centers, leisure and educational institutions.
The console spawned various versions depending on the material stock.
A successor was planned, but not released.